{"tid":1007312,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[M記隊長]Yon-Rogg/Mar-Vell原是奇洛李維斯而非祖迪羅","createTime":"2019-02-03T16:14:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T04:31:56.000Z","uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"51d22b6726a7d475338dc38b6b8b03471c34dcfa","tid":1007312,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T16:14:55.000Z","msg":"[FB page：Marvel &amp; DC Fans 粉絲]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《Marvel 隊長》祖迪羅的角色新聞不斷，除了被傳過他戲裏身分是Yon-Rogg，亦有傳聞說他其實是Mar-Vell。而日前，有報導說原來這個角色選祖迪羅演之前，Marvel Studios曾經考慮過奇洛李維斯，最後因為奇洛本人為拍《殺神3》而不能同期拍攝《Marvel 隊長》，但相信《殺神3》亦會是他很重要的里程碑，要不然大家便能在MCU目睹奇洛真身！<br />\n其實奇洛他亦曾經表示過有興趣再拍超級英雄片，希望繼在2005年的《Constantine》(DC Comics)後，他能再次出演超級英雄電影。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cinemablend.com/news/2466283/mcu-recruit-keanu-reeves-reportedly-dropped-captain-marvel-role-for-john-wick-3?fbclid=IwAR3Ncyx7yQee57W4dzQcHl2Wk2v8FIW98wiiOSP_-FW6uFNJBc5ToP067Sk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cinemablend.com%2Fnews%2F2466283%2Fmcu-recruit-keanu-reeves-reportedly-dropped-captain-marvel-role-for-john-wick-3%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3Ncyx7yQee57W4dzQcHl2Wk2v8FIW98wiiOSP_-FW6uFNJBc5ToP067Sk&d=GmsUkepvXW4IpX0DHJvToDbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=36703e83\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cinemablend.com/news/2466283/mcu-recruit-keanu-reeves-reportedly-dropped-captain-marvel-role-for-john-wick-3?fbclid=IwAR3Ncyx7yQee57W4dzQcHl2Wk2v8FIW98wiiOSP_-FW6uFNJBc5ToP067Sk</a>"},{"pid":"2407d77b956ffe9177753422f66e589ce2b21c68","tid":1007312,"uid":18697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T01:57:47.000Z","msg":"睇錯標題係Yon-Rogg/Mar-Vell原來是..."},{"pid":"bf07cb64ac191fcc2a5d1d198ad5cc130ac4fcf5","tid":1007312,"uid":21922,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T02:21:51.000Z","msg":"奇洛話過自己想做蝙蝠俠同狼人，最鐘意嘅超級英雄就係Wolverine<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你好想Constantine出第二集<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=